fields.name: Addmetocart Solid Women’s All Women Are Created Equal, But The Best Are Born In November Navy Hoodie Sweatshirt
points: Fit Type: Regular Fit
Fabric: Ultimate fashion t-shirt meticulously crafted with 100% Cotton Fabric with 320 GSM thickness.
Color: Navy, Sleeve: Half, Neck: Round Neck. Checkout our storefront for male combination.
Size: Small, Medium, Large, X-Large, 2X-Large. Bust size 34-36 can go for S, 36.5-38 can go for M, 39-41 can go for L, 42-43.5 can go for XL and 44-46 can go for XXL.
Quality: All garments are subjected to the following tests: Fabric dimensional stability test and quality inspection for colors and bio washed for extra softness.

Fabric Care: Delicate machine wash. Use mild detergent, wash, dry and iron Inside out. Do not wring, do not dry in direct sunlight, do not scrub, do not iron directly on print and embroidery, do not tumble dry, do not dry clean,do not bleach.
